[0.001, "o", "\u001b[1;39m{\r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"id\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"1\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"jsonrpc\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"2.0\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n  \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"result\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m{\r\n    \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"artifacts\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m[\r\n      \u001b[1;39m{\r\n        \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"artifactId\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"517db393-2ab4-4a91-a37b-1f52530e7fe9\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n        \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"parts\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m[\r\n          \u001b[1;39m{\r\n            \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"kind\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"text\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "            \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"text\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"The following AI agents are currently deployed in the cluster:\\n\\n1.  **k8s-inspector**\\n    *   **Framework:** kagent\\n    *   **Description:** A read-only Kubernetes cluster inspector.\\n    *   **Tools:** It has access to various diagnostic tools, including cluster configuration, resource retrieval, logs, and service connectivity checks.\\n    *   **Model:** gemini-3.1-flash-lite (via agentgateway)\\n\\n2.  **ai-infra-advisor** (This agent)\\n    *   **Framework:** Google ADK\\n    *   **Description:** Your AI infrastructure advisor.\\n    *   **Model:** gemini-3.1-flash-lite (via agentgateway)\\n\\nLet me know if you would like more details about a specific agent or if you'd like to explore the infrastructure components further!\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n          \u001b[1;39m}\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n        \u001b[1;39m]\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n      \u001b[1;39m}\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m\r\n    \u001b[1;39m]\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n    \u001b[0m\u001b[1;34m\"contextId\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m: \u001b[0m\u001b[0;32m\"3de77c1f-fc86-4e48-b3eb-e71688300c6f\"\u001b[0m\u001b[1;39m,\r\n"]
